"title": "4506: seed",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4506: seed",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The means of propagating life from one generation to another. Figuratively, the term illustrates principles of spiritual life and growth, especially in later parts of the OT and throughout the NT.</p>\n<h2>How seed was used</h2>\n<h3>Seed for eating</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:29\">GEN 1:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen42:1-Gen42:2\">GEN 42:1–42:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh5:1-Neh5:2\">NEH 5:1–5:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:28\">ISA 28:28</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl11:6\">ECC 11:6</a></p>\n<h3>Seed as an offering</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:15-Lev23:21\">LEV 23:15–23:21</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num28:26-Num28:31\">NUM 28:26–28:31</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr31:5\">2CH 31:5</a></p>\n<h3>Seed to measure value</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev27:16\">LEV 27:16</a></p>\n<h2>How seed was appreciated</h2>\n<h3>The presence of seed was a blessing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech8:12\">ZEC 8:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen8:22\">GEN 8:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps67:6\">PSA 67:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps85:12\">PSA 85:12</a></p>\n<h3>The absence of seed was a curse</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel1:16-Joel1:17\">JOL 1:16–1:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:38-Deut28:42\">DEU 28:38–28:42</a></p>\n<h2>Regulations in the law concerning seed</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:9\">DEU 22:9</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:19\">LEV 19:19</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev11:37-Lev11:38\">LEV 11:37–11:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev27:30\">LEV 27:30</a></p>\n<h2>Seed used figuratively to illustrate kingdom life</h2>\n<h3>To illustrate those ready to enter the kingdom of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:35-John4:38\">JHN 4:35–4:38</a></strong></p>\n<h3>To illustrate birth into eternal life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:23\">1PE 1:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:9\">1JN 3:9</a></p>\n<h3>To illustrate the growth of the kingdom of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:31-Matt13:32\">MAT 13:31–13:32</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:30-Mark4:32\">MRK 4:30–4:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:18-Luke13:19\">LUK 13:18–13:19</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:26-Mark4:29\">MRK 4:26–4:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:24-Matt13:30\">MAT 13:24–13:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:36-Matt13:43\">MAT 13:36–13:43</a></p>\n<h3>To illustrate the growth of the church</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:6-1Cor3:7\">1CO 3:6–3:7</a></strong></p>\n<h3>To illustrate God's word and people's response to it</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:1-Matt13:23\">MAT 13:1–13:23</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:1-Mark4:20\">MRK 4:1–4:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:4-Luke8:15\">LUK 8:4–8:15</a> <em>the parable of the sower</em></p>\n<h3>To illustrate faith</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:20\">MAT 17:20</a></strong></p>\n<h3>To illustrate the principle that death comes before life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:23-John12:25\">JHN 12:23–12:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:36\">1CO 15:36</a></p>\n<h3>To illustrate the resurrection body</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:35-1Cor15:38\">1CO 15:35–15:38</a></strong></p>\n<h2>God calls his people to sow seeds of righteousness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:18\">JAS 3:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps126:5-Ps126:6\">PSA 126:5–126:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:8\">PRO 22:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:3-Jer4:4\">JER 4:3–4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos10:12\">HOS 10:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:6\">2CO 9:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor9:10\">2CO 9:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:7-Gal6:9\">GAL 6:7–6:9</a></p>",
